    <para id="id1171433404195">Each of the hydrides is prepared by the reaction of acid on a metal chalcogenide, e.g., <link target-id="eip-32"/> and <link target-id="eip-481"/>. The unstable H<sub>2</sub>Po has been prepared by the reaction of HCl on Po metal. </para>
    
    <equation id="eip-32"><media id="id1171431709203_media" alt="">
